.6&#x000b1;0.9</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">11.2&#x000b1;1.2</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">p-value</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.01</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.01</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.001</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.05</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.001</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.001</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.001</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.001</td></tr></tbody></table><table-wrap-foot><fn><p>CI: central incisor, MA: mouth angle, VC: vocal cord.</p></fn></table-wrap-foot></table-wrap><table-wrap id="T3" position="float"><label>Table-III</label><caption><p>Correlations of height and age against airway length.</p></caption><table frame="hsides" rules="groups" width="100%"><thead><tr><th align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"/><th align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><italic>Men (P)</italic></th><th align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><italic>Women (P)</italic></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left" colspan="3" rowspan="1"><italic>Correlation between Height and Airway Length</italic></td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;Mouth Angle - Carina</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c; 0.01</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c; 0.01</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;Mouth Angle - Epiglottis</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c; 0.01</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c; 0.05</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;Epiglottis-Vocal Cord</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003e; 0.05</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003e; 0.05</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x02003;Vocal Cord - Carina</td><td align="left" rowspan="